Wolf Child

**Name**: (No name)
**Gender**: Male
**Race**: Human
**Age**: 9
**Appearance**: All he is wearing is two giant leaves tied together by a thin fine, used for his belt. He doesn't have a shirt or shoes. He has neon green eyes, which seem to glow, he also has long black hair. His teeth are somehow managed to be pure white, and the only thing he eats is animals and all he drinks is water.
**Relatives**: His wolf pack.
**Friends/Enemies**: His parents
**Backstory**: He was left alone in the woods, but then wolves decided to take him in. He can barely speak or act like a human, but what he does know he takes advantage of.
**Other**: Shy,Insecure,strong and has hard time making friends.
**RPs Used For**: Any kind
